data.description: Step inside this cozy, move in ready ranch home and discover an inviting living space that's perfect for relaxing or entertaining. This home offers 3 nicely sized bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The kitchen has granite countertops and is ready for your culinary endeavors! Home also features a large, flat and fully fenced in back yard perfect for an upcoming Winter bonfire. Roof and HVAC replaced in 2022. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, looking to downsize, or searching for an investment opportunity this gem is a must-see.
